line_1: And now the matchless deed's atchiev'd,
Numb'ring the Wonders which That Youth atchiev'd,
line_2: Spain, from th'Usurper Bourbon's Arms retriev'd,

line_1: Show all the Spoils by valiant Kings achiev'd,
line_2: And groaning Nations by Their Arms reliev'd;

line_1: My full Design with vast Expence atchiev'd,
line_2: I came, beheld, admir'd, reflected, griev'd.
